com.ece.superkids.users.entities

Class History

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ece.superkids.users.entities.History
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class History
extends Object
implements Serializable
    The History class represents the current state of the user. It maintains the history for all the questions and the scores the user answered, up to 5 attempts.
    Author:
    Marc Adam
